_sText:
I made some significant changes from B1, so I figured I'd put this up for revote.

This is my first map in Hammer.  It's a little bit iceworld, a little bit aim_shotty.  I tried to keep everything open and easy to navigate while discouraging camping.  This map is fast, furious and fun.

Beta1 -> Beta3 changes:
Added 3d Skybox
Changed Layout
Added Displacement to Base Terrain
Added Ladders
Added Distance Fog
Changed Textures

This version features the final layout.  Any future changes will be cosmetic or very, very minor.
